						<summary>

						<p>Above the entrance into the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of a cavern on a hill.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vijaya.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription engraved in characters of about the 16th century and records the gift of a <hi rend="italic">maṭha</hi> called <hi rend="italic">Nīlakaṇṭha-nāyaṉār-maṭha</hi> to a certain Sāmantaya-nāyakkar for the merit of one Timmā-nāyakkar. The name of the donor is not mentioned in the record. </p>						

						</summary>
